      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i keep getting a MemoryError when i try to run this pandas script on a large csv. i'm currently using a list comprehension to process certain columns but it's just crashing my machine. should i be using generator functions instead to save on memory?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
